00:59:00,203 --> 00:59:04,879
I think your companions don't like
to mingle with people like us.

552
00:59:06,843 --> 00:59:07,913
Not at all.

553
00:59:08,078 --> 00:59:10,285
Please don't take any offense.

554
00:59:10,614 --> 00:59:13,823
They're both afraid of large crowds.

555
00:59:14,084 --> 00:59:16,997
Call it middle-aged shyness if you like.

556
00:59:18,422 --> 00:59:21,767
Is the weapon safe? Is it still stable?

557
00:59:21,958 --> 00:59:25,804
I heard it had sustained
considerable damage last night.

558
00:59:26,363 --> 00:59:28,639
I'm impressed by your intel.

559
00:59:29,032 --> 00:59:34,539
Intel is my trade. You know I'm the best.

560
00:59:34,971 --> 00:59:36,575
They're paying a lot of money

561
00:59:36,740 --> 00:59:38,947
for the cop who killed the brother.

562
00:59:39,342 --> 00:59:45,850
If I can get information on who the cop is,

563
00:59:47,250 --> 00:59:49,287
can you tell me more about Helios?

564
00:59:49,453 --> 00:59:55,631
Allow me and my business to offer you
and your boys a little friendly advice.

565
00:59:56,293 --> 01:00:00,605
Do not turn Hong Kong into a battlefield.

566
01:00:00,797 --> 01:00:02,640
I don't care how you do it.

567
01:00:02,833 --> 01:00:09,011
Get this bomb out of my
city as soon as possible.

568
01:00:09,306 --> 01:00:11,217
You got it?

569
01:00:21,818 --> 01:00:23,297
Please take a look at this.

570
01:00:24,488 --> 01:00:25,296
What is it?

571
01:00:25,455 --> 01:00:27,958
You wanted me to dig up
everything on Helios.

572
01:00:32,028 --> 01:00:35,009
The Japanese Imperial Household Agency
gave him that name.

573
01:00:35,432 --> 01:00:38,174
12 years ago, someone broke into
the Imperial Palace in Tokyo

574
01:00:38,335 --> 01:00:41,145
and stole one of the three
Imperial Regalia of Japan,

575
01:00:41,304 --> 01:00:43,841
the jewel Yasakani no Magatama.

576
01:00:44,141 --> 01:00:47,452
He became an international arms dealer
after he left Japan.

577
01:00:47,677 --> 01:00:49,247
The U.S. suspects he has,
over the past decade,

578
01:00:49,412 --> 01:00:51,358
orchestrated at least 3 arms deals in Asia.

579
01:00:51,515 --> 01:00:53,426
He managed to getaway every time.

580
01:00:54,317 --> 01:00:56,456
It's possible Hong Kong
is one of his bases.

581
01:00:58,088 --> 01:01:00,932
With someone good at attack,
his enemy won't know what to defend.

582
01:01:01,158 --> 01:01:04,469
With someone good at defense,
his enemy won't know what to attack.

583
01:01:05,362 --> 01:01:07,171
You mean...

584
01:01:08,665 --> 01:01:11,839
Tell the weapon experts in Beijing to
stand by and be prepared to come at once.

585
01:01:28,051 --> 01:01:31,260
We have some information
from the CIA regarding Middle East.

586
01:01:31,555 --> 01:01:35,264
They have got some mass destructive weapon
they are using against civilians.

587
01:01:35,859 --> 01:01:37,668
This is all the information we received.

588
01:01:37,827 --> 01:01:38,601
Excuse me.

589
01:01:38,762 --> 01:01:39,638
No problem.

590
01:01:45,235 --> 01:01:48,739
Eric, someone is rounding
up firearms in Macau

591
01:01:48,905 --> 01:01:51,044
and shipping them to Hong Kong.

592
01:02:10,660 --> 01:02:12,105
Something came up at the university.

593
01:02:12,262 --> 01:02:14,003
Can I call my secretary Angela?

594
01:02:14,164 --> 01:02:15,507
Hurry.

595
01:02:16,299 --> 01:02:17,972
Put it through.

596
01:02:28,078 --> 01:02:30,922
Mr. Fan, we're underground.
Can you hear me?

597
01:02:31,081 --> 01:02:32,458
Go ahead.

598
01:02:32,682 --> 01:02:34,252
Good.

599
01:02:34,484 --> 01:02:37,397
We'll start the safety check.

600
01:02:52,802 --> 01:02:57,808
Mr. Fan, I have a reading of 1250 msv.

601
01:02:58,041 --> 01:02:59,384
My assistant is down.

602
01:02:59,542 --> 01:03:00,953
Call the Fire Department
and get an ambulance right away.

603
01:03:01,111 --> 01:03:02,112
Do you COPY?

604
01:03:02,279 --> 01:03:03,781
Tracy, call the Fire Department
and get an ambulance right away.

605
01:03:03,947 --> 01:03:05,017
Yes, sir.

606
01:03:32,342 --> 01:03:34,253
Have you contacted Colonel Choi?

607
01:03:34,844 --> 01:03:35,845
Their phones are off.

608
01:03:36,012 --> 01:03:38,288
Control is trying to locate them.

609
01:03:42,652 --> 01:03:44,563
Here's a graphite case

610
01:03:44,821 --> 01:03:46,164
that can last 3 hours.

611
01:03:46,323 --> 01:03:47,927
I have another one.

612
01:03:48,124 --> 01:03:48,829
As soon as you find them,

613
01:03:48,992 --> 01:03:50,232
ship this thing out right away.

614
01:03:50,360 --> 01:03:52,499
It's not going anywhere.

615
01:03:54,264 --> 01:03:55,675
This weapon is leaking.

616
01:03:55,832 --> 01:03:57,903
Do you care about the lives
of Hong Kong people?

617
01:03:58,168 --> 01:04:00,546
This is precisely what I'm doing.

618
01:04:00,837 --> 01:04:03,181
Have you forgotten what I told you?

619
01:04:03,740 --> 01:04:05,549
Mr. Fan, I don't care anymore.

620
01:04:05,709 --> 01:04:06,881
There's nothing I can do.

621
01:04:07,043 --> 01:04:09,216
The weapon specialists from Beijing
will be here soon.

622
01:04:09,879 --> 01:04:11,552
If the professor doesn't want to help us,

623
01:04:11,715 --> 01:04:13,251
and I mean "if",

624
01:04:13,850 --> 01:04:16,729
give us a bit more time
and we can take over.

625
01:04:19,255 --> 01:04:21,428
Ridiculous.

626
01:04:27,130 --> 01:04:28,632
- Professor.
- Shui up.

627
01:04:28,798 --> 01:04:30,368
- I know.
- Enough.

628
01:04:31,201 --> 01:04:33,545
I can't accept him.

629
01:04:34,137 --> 01:04:36,048
I can't work with him.

630
01:04:36,706 --> 01:04:38,208
I know.

631
01:04:38,508 --> 01:04:39,953
So stubborn!

632
01:05:24,320 --> 01:05:27,460
Sorry, we're closed. Come back at 6.

633
01:05:28,458 --> 01:05:31,371
Are those the books for the restaurant
or from the arms deals?

634
01:05:42,405 --> 01:05:44,385
How long has it been?

635
01:05:45,875 --> 01:05:47,616
Almost 20 years.

636
01:05:50,713 --> 01:05:53,091
The day you opened this joint,

637
01:05:53,750 --> 01:05:55,730
I didn't have time to drop by.

638
01:05:56,553 --> 01:05:58,430
You head up a department now?

639
01:06:02,225 --> 01:06:04,171
And I thought you had retired.

640
01:06:05,962 --> 01:06:08,499
You know I always do the cooking.

641
01:06:08,798 --> 01:06:11,335
Let's cut to the chase.

642
01:06:12,469 --> 01:06:15,177
How nice of you to drop by. Have you eaten?

643
01:06:15,338 --> 01:06:17,215
Let me fix you something.

644
01:06:24,581 --> 01:06:26,390
Sit down.

645
01:06:31,721 --> 01:06:36,693
Two nights ago, we busted an arms deal.

646
01:06:37,193 --> 01:06:40,299
Both parties should be rather antsy by now.

647
01:06:40,797 --> 01:06:42,174
My informer tells me

648
01:06:42,332 --> 01:06:45,575
the buyer is so pissed

649
01:06:46,002 --> 01:06:47,982
he ordered firearms from Macau

650
01:06:48,238 --> 01:06:50,718
to go to war with the Hong Kong Police.

651
01:06:52,575 --> 01:06:55,556
I can only think of you,

652
01:06:56,079 --> 01:07:00,050
who can fill such a huge order in Macau.

653
01:07:02,085 --> 01:07:03,894
Where is Helios?

654
01:07:18,968 --> 01:07:20,743
Mr. Lee,

655
01:07:21,237 --> 01:07:23,581
you lost me.

656
01:07:30,046 --> 01:07:32,219
I'll make it simple for you.

657
01:07:33,082 --> 01:07:37,087
After I stepped inside this restaurant,

658
01:07:37,787 --> 01:07:41,462
nothing in here belongs to you anymore.

659
01:07:42,458 --> 01:07:44,597
Including your life.

660
01:07:58,541 --> 01:08:00,885
You work hard

661
01:08:01,344 --> 01:08:04,882
to give your family the good life, right?

662
01:08:10,420 --> 01:08:15,233
If you touch my granddaughter,
I guarantee you'll die horribly.

663
01:08:15,558 --> 01:08:18,004
If you come with me quietly,

664
01:08:18,461 --> 01:08:21,635
I guarantee your family will be safe.

665
01:08:26,235 --> 01:08:27,805
They're taking Sophia to Hong Kong.

666
01:08:27,971 --> 01:08:30,850
Once she gets inside that car,

667
01:08:31,007 --> 01:08:32,145
she'll be blamed for any deal
that goes sour from now on.

668
01:08:32,308 --> 01:08:33,548
She will never tell on us.

669
01:08:33,710 --> 01:08:34,688
It's the rule, what we believe

670
01:08:34,844 --> 01:08:37,085
is not what other people will believe.

671
01:08:39,749 --> 01:08:41,422
When she decided to go with Eric Lee,

672
01:08:41,584 --> 01:08:43,757
she was prepared to die.

673
01:11:57,213 --> 01:11:58,851
Don'! Move!

674
01:12:03,486 --> 01:12:05,898
Calm down, Mr. Lee.

675
01:12:11,928 --> 01:12:13,339
Take her away.

676
01:12:56,239 --> 01:13:00,187
Sin Mi Kyung, since we left the temple,

677
01:13:00,343 --> 01:13:01,583
you wanted us to keep our phones off

678
01:13:01,744 --> 01:13:03,417
and took us around in circles.

679
01:13:03,713 --> 01:13:05,784
What's going on?

680
01:13:12,788 --> 01:13:14,267
Our DC8

681
01:13:14,423 --> 01:13:16,425
has alerted the UK, US, China

682
01:13:16,759 --> 01:13:19,433
and half of Middle East.

683
01:13:19,629 --> 01:13:22,473
Because it's detained,
they say in addition to Helios,

684
01:13:22,632 --> 01:13:26,079
at least 3 other parties will launch
a terrorist attack on Hong Kong.

685
01:13:28,337 --> 01:13:31,511
If we hand over the cop
who killed the Middle Eastern buyer,

686
01:13:32,775 --> 01:13:34,948
they'll tell us where to find Helios.

687
01:13:36,512 --> 01:13:38,253
That's simple enough.

688
01:13:38,915 --> 01:13:41,225
Explain to Inspector Fan,

689
01:13:41,584 --> 01:13:44,087
and tell him to do the trade.
What's the problem?

690
01:13:46,589 --> 01:13:49,297
Are you suggesting we betray
the Hong Kong Police?

691
01:13:49,458 --> 01:13:53,304
Use Inspector Fan to exchange
for unconfirmed intel?

692
01:14:06,175 --> 01:14:07,745
Inspector Fan is a cop.

693
01:14:08,010 --> 01:14:11,719
He should be prepared
to die for his country.

694
01:14:11,881 --> 01:14:14,191
If I were in his shoes,

695
01:14:14,450 --> 01:14:16,452
I would have done the same at all costs.

696
01:14:16,786 --> 01:14:19,266
This is not about trading
one life for another.

697
01:14:19,422 --> 01:14:21,561
This is about trustworthiness.

698
01:14:21,958 --> 01:14:25,633
What you're doing is
no different from those criminals.

699
01:14:36,572 --> 01:14:38,210
Sacrificing one life

700
01:14:38,474 --> 01:14:40,454
can save many others.

701
01:14:40,609 --> 01:14:43,089
Didn't you say we must get the weapon back?

702
01:14:43,245 --> 01:14:44,690
Even by force?

703
01:14:44,847 --> 01:14:46,292
I have deployed my men.

704
01:14:46,449 --> 01:14:48,129
Why are you so indecisive all of a sudden?

705
01:14:48,150 --> 01:14:50,130
I only told you to get ready

706
01:14:50,319 --> 01:14:51,662
just in case.

707
01:14:51,821 --> 01:14:53,095
Just in case?

708
01:14:58,627 --> 01:15:00,800
If the informer is reliable,

709
01:15:01,163 --> 01:15:03,507
we missed Helios by a few inches.

710
01:15:03,666 --> 01:15:05,304
We would have

711
01:15:05,501 --> 01:15:08,380
let the generals down.

712
01:15:08,838 --> 01:15:10,408
How can you face them?

713
01:15:14,510 --> 01:15:16,114
Hold on.

714
01:15:16,579 --> 01:15:18,217
Can I say something?

715
01:15:18,381 --> 01:15:22,056
Colonel Choi, your decision is immature.

716
01:15:36,699 --> 01:15:39,043
Turn your phones back on.

717
01:15:45,508 --> 01:15:46,680
There's something wrong with your weapon.

718
01:15:46,842 --> 01:15:49,015
Everyone must report back
to the intel center.

719
01:15:59,622 --> 01:16:02,569
Chinese weapon experts are coming to
Hong Kong, arriving in 30 minutes.

720
01:16:02,958 --> 01:16:04,938
I'm sending you a file.

721
01:16:05,127 --> 01:16:08,040
When you see the breaking news,
forward it 10 CTRU.

722
01:16:18,140 --> 01:16:20,381
When the Hong Kong Police intercepted DC8,

723
01:16:20,543 --> 01:16:22,716
we have examined it carefully.

724
01:16:22,912 --> 01:16:25,256
The bullet did not damage the inside.

725
01:16:25,748 --> 01:16:29,093
After authentication,
we activated the insulation mode.

726
01:16:29,251 --> 01:16:31,492
It's impossible to have a radiation leak.

727
01:16:31,654 --> 01:16:33,600
You're saying...

728
01:16:35,124 --> 01:16:39,800
The Professor is helping us.

729
01:17:38,954 --> 01:17:40,490
We sent her blood sample to the lab.

730
01:17:40,656 --> 01:17:42,567
We'll know in 8 hours

731
01:17:42,725 --> 01:17:44,762
if she's the missing flight attendant.

732
01:18:22,865 --> 01:18:24,708
Drink some water.

733
01:18:38,747 --> 01:18:40,590
How old are you?

734
01:18:42,251 --> 01:18:43,753
24?

735
01:18:46,088 --> 01:18:47,726
26?

736
01:18:50,926 --> 01:18:52,599
You should be sensible.

737
01:18:56,432 --> 01:18:58,241
You still have a choice.

738
01:19:00,903 --> 01:19:02,007
Either,

739
01:19:02,171 --> 01:19:04,583
a life sentence,

740
01:19:05,074 --> 01:19:06,246
<i>or,</i>

741
01:19:06,408 --> 01:19:08,354
help us find your boss.

742
01:19:13,582 --> 01:19:17,291
Forget about turning state witness
and a reduced sentence.

743
01:19:17,653 --> 01:19:21,294
You squeal on him and you walk.

744
01:19:21,790 --> 01:19:24,293
I'll send you wherever you want to go.

745
01:19:59,962 --> 01:20:01,498
Mr. Lee.

746
01:20:03,666 --> 01:20:05,668
Think ii over.

747
01:20:24,553 --> 01:20:26,396
We're at the race track right now.

748
01:20:26,555 --> 01:20:29,001
Allegedly, there was an
explosion 20 minutes ago.

749
01:20:29,158 --> 01:20:30,865
Over 20 people were injured.

750
01:20:31,026 --> 01:20:34,303
The bomb squad has been
summoned to the scene.

751
01:20:34,463 --> 01:20:36,500
As you can see, many racing fans...

752
01:20:41,070 --> 01:20:42,674
Somewhere on the stand behind me

753
01:20:42,838 --> 01:20:44,715
exploded.

754
01:20:49,945 --> 01:20:51,549
This is just the beginning.

755
01:20:51,714 --> 01:20:55,059
Hand over the weapon and
the hostage in an hour

756
01:20:55,217 --> 01:20:58,790
to Causeway Bay on your own,

757
01:20:58,954 --> 01:21:02,458
or else start preparing
for massive casualties.

758
01:21:07,162 --> 01:21:08,505
If you wish,

759
01:21:08,664 --> 01:21:11,270
with an invitation from
your Chief Executive,

760
01:21:12,067 --> 01:21:14,240
our PLA in the Hong Kong
Garrison can be deployed.

761
01:21:17,406 --> 01:21:18,908
Do you realize you're out of control?

762
01:21:19,074 --> 01:21:20,553
Listen...

763
01:21:20,909 --> 01:21:22,946
before you have a grasp on what's going on,

764
01:21:23,112 --> 01:21:26,025
we have already declared war on Helios.

765
01:21:26,415 --> 01:21:27,587
If you compromise,

766
01:21:27,750 --> 01:21:29,821
he'll turn Hong Kong into

767
01:21:29,985 --> 01:21:31,828
a hub for arms deal.

768
01:21:31,987 --> 01:21:33,227
You want that?

769
01:21:33,389 --> 01:21:37,269
Hold on a second. I actually
got another solution.

770
01:21:37,659 --> 01:21:38,660
According to my informer,

771
01:21:38,827 --> 01:21:40,428
he can give me the whereabouts of Helios

772
01:21:40,429 --> 01:21:42,773
if we give him the officer

773
01:21:43,632 --> 01:21:45,339
who shot the Middle Eastern buyer,

774
01:21:45,534 --> 01:21:47,514
who happens to be Inspector Fan.

775
01:21:48,804 --> 01:21:51,375
Is your informer clean?

776
01:21:51,740 --> 01:21:53,515
He was the one

777
01:21:53,675 --> 01:21:56,781
who told us the location of
the deal two nights ago.

778
01:21:58,080 --> 01:21:59,582
I killed the guy.

779
01:21:59,882 --> 01:22:03,796
I don't really mean to hand you over.

780
01:22:04,052 --> 01:22:05,929
But if we make contact,

781
01:22:06,088 --> 01:22:08,796
maybe we can find Helios.

782
01:22:12,461 --> 01:22:14,304
Can you manage?

783
01:22:15,030 --> 01:22:16,634
Sure.

784
01:22:17,032 --> 01:22:18,375
- Wai Yip.
- Yes.

785
01:22:18,534 --> 01:22:20,494
Get <i>2</i> teams ready to go
with me for the handover.

786
01:22:20,502 --> 01:22:21,981
Yes, Sir.

787
01:22:23,639 --> 01:22:25,641
Professor, Mr. Choi,

788
01:22:25,808 --> 01:22:28,015
please double check DC8.

789
01:22:34,283 --> 01:22:35,626
Where are we going?

790
01:22:35,784 --> 01:22:37,627
We're going to Macau.

791
01:23:28,504 --> 01:23:29,847
Thank you, Professor.

792
01:23:30,005 --> 01:23:30,983
For what?

793
01:23:31,139 --> 01:23:33,176
I come from a family of scientists.

794
01:23:33,408 --> 01:23:35,046
I'm willing to swear by my family

795
01:23:35,210 --> 01:23:36,621
and my brother's name

796
01:23:36,778 --> 01:23:39,258
this is the safest weapon ever built.

797
01:23:40,282 --> 01:23:42,159
I already told Eric Lee.

798
01:23:42,451 --> 01:23:45,796
I'll leave after debriefing
you upon your return.

799
01:23:46,788 --> 01:23:48,392
The sooner DC8 leaves,

800
01:23:48,557 --> 01:23:50,161
the sooner Hong Kong will be safe.

801
01:23:50,993 --> 01:23:53,132
Do what you have to do

802
01:23:53,362 --> 01:23:55,137
and you'll be doing us a favor.

803
01:24:38,874 --> 01:24:40,683
Even inside the graphite case,

804
01:24:40,842 --> 01:24:42,515
absolutely no more collision.

805
01:24:42,678 --> 01:24:44,749
Handle it with your utmost care.

806
01:24:46,281 --> 01:24:47,282
Lieutenant Park,

807
01:24:47,449 --> 01:24:49,122
I have something to do. I need your help.

808
01:24:49,284 --> 01:24:50,262
Yes, Sir.

809
01:24:50,419 --> 01:24:51,921
Mr. Choi.

810
01:25:19,114 --> 01:25:21,025
Stay calm.

811
01:25:22,050 --> 01:25:23,996
Any monkey business from you,

812
01:25:26,488 --> 01:25:28,126
and you're the first one I'll shoot.

813
01:26:48,336 --> 01:26:49,747
Saad.

814
01:26:50,205 --> 01:26:52,378
Saad, I brought them here.

815
01:26:52,841 --> 01:26:54,548
Saad.

816
01:27:38,954 --> 01:27:39,762
Say it.

817
01:27:39,921 --> 01:27:40,899
Change location.

818
01:27:41,056 --> 01:27:43,969
Sunshine Plaza on Jaffe Road in Wanchai.

819
