940
01:43:18,759 --> 01:43:20,932
Helios is always one step ahead of us.

941
01:43:32,573 --> 01:43:34,575
Helios?

942
01:43:41,282 --> 01:43:44,593
The Americans and Koreans failed to
nail you all these years.

943
01:43:45,619 --> 01:43:47,758
I feel so honored.

944
01:43:48,956 --> 01:43:51,334
You knew I was Helios,
and yet you came alone.

945
01:43:51,792 --> 01:43:53,669
Song An is still around.

946
01:43:53,928 --> 01:43:55,874
No matter how certain I am,

947
01:43:56,130 --> 01:43:58,633
