948
01:44:03,070 --> 01:44:05,175
Your personality is your downfall.

949
01:44:05,573 --> 01:44:07,018
You want to be the Commissioner?

950
01:44:07,241 --> 01:44:08,914
Him?

951
01:44:11,011 --> 01:44:15,517
