966
01:47:50,998 --> 01:47:52,636
Colonel Choi,

967
01:47:53,167 --> 01:47:58,167
thank you for your good work. Welcome home!

968
01:48:14,922 --> 01:48:19,268
Colonel Choi Min Ho reporting to

969
01:48:20,594 --> 01:48:26,875
the General and NIS Director.

970
01:48:55,763 --> 01:48:57,538
