971
01:48:57,698 --> 01:49:01,077
Professor Siu Chi Yan is
not Vietnamese Chinese.

972
01:49:01,502 --> 01:49:03,539
According to INTERPOL intel,

973
01:49:03,704 --> 01:49:06,548
his 2 messengers and a black market buyer

974
01:49:06,707 --> 01:49:08,550
called His Majesty

975
01:49:08,742 --> 01:49:11,052
were last seen in Estonia.

976
01:49:11,712 --> 01:49:12,713
This is where we suspect

977
01:49:12,913 --> 01:49:15,587
